<section class="brand-- brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="featured-documents">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">Featured</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

      <div class="gem-c-image-card gem-c-image-card--large ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="20 years of the national minimum wage. A history of the UK minimum wage and its effects. April 2019." src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/69822/s712_20th_anniv_cover.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-04-01"> 1 April 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Press release</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/news/20-years-of-the-national-minimum-wage-have-boosted-pay-by-5000">20 years of the National Minimum Wage have boosted pay by £5,000</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>On the 20th anniversary of the National Minimum Wage, a new report by the Low Pay Commission examines how the policy has transformed the UK labour market.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>


    <div class="grid-row">
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="LPC logo" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/69510/s465_2019_consultation.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-03-14">14 March 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Open consultation</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/consultations/low-pay-commission-consultation-2019">Low Pay Commission consultation 2019</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The Low Pay Commission is gathering evidence in support of its 2019 report.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="2019 rates" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/67414/s465_2019_rates_pic_WEB.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-01-11">11 January 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Research and analysis</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/publications/national-minimum-wage-low-pay-commission-2018-report">National Minimum Wage: Low Pay Commission 2018 Report</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The Low Pay Commission’s (LPC) 2018 Report, containing analysis and evidence underpinning the LPC’s National Living Wage and National Minimum Wage recommendations.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
            <div class="gem-c-image-card  ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="2019 rates" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/67413/s465_2019_rates_pic_WEB.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2018-11-27">27 November 2018</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Press release</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/news/up-to-5-million-workers-benefited-from-the-national-living-wage-in-2018">Up to 5 million workers benefited from the National Living Wage in 2018</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The Low Pay Commission’s 2018 Report, published today, finds that increases to the National Living Wage (NLW) raised the pay of up to 5 million workers this year.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

